---

<section
  class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[75vh] py-20 px-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-delfos-bg-dark via-delfos-black/70 to-black/80 dark:from-delfos-bg-light dark:via-gold/10 dark:to-delfos-bg-dark overflow-hidden text-center"
>
  {/* Overlay visual dorado, tendencia editorial */}
  <svg
    aria-hidden="true"
    width="620"
    height="620"
    class="absolute -top-32 -left-32 opacity-25 blur-2xl pointer-events-none select-none"
  >
    <circle cx="310" cy="310" r="270" fill="#C2A875"></circle>
  </svg>
  <img
    src="/assets/logos/delfos-logo-transparente.png"
    alt="Logo Delfos Studio"
    class="w-32 md:w-40 mb-10 drop-shadow-2xl animate-fadein pointer-events-none select-none"
    loading="lazy"
    style="animation-delay:.05s"
  />
  <h1
    class="font-serif-title text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight relative animate-fadein"
    style="animation-delay:.2s"
  >
    Convertimos <span
      class="text-gold relative after:absolute after:left-0 after:-bottom-2 after:w-full after:h-2 after:bg-gold/30 after:rounded-full after:animate-glow"
      >ideas</span
    > en <span class="text-gold">experiencias digitales</span>
  </h1>
  <p
    class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-2xl text-delfos-bg-light/90 dark:text-delfos-black/70 mb-10 animate-fadein"
    style="animation-delay:.4s"
  >
    Agencia creativa de dise침o web, branding visual, automatizaci칩n, SEO y
    gesti칩n de contenido. Impulsamos marcas para el futuro.
  </p>
  <a
    href="#contacto"
    class="inline-block bg-gold/90 hover:bg-gold text-delfos-bg-dark dark:text-delfos-bg-light px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg shadow-gold-glow hover:scale-105 focus-visible:ring-2 ring-gold transition-all duration-300 animate-fadein"
    style="animation-delay:.6s"
  >
    Hablemos de tu proyecto
  </a>
</section>

<style is:global>
  @keyframes fadein {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(40px) scale(0.98);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: none;
    }
  }
  @keyframes glow {
    0%,
    100% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px 0 #c2a87599;
    }
    50% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 24px 8px #c2a875bb;
    }
  }
  .animate-fadein {
    animation: fadein 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.5, 1.3, 0.5, 1.1) both;
  }
  .after\:animate-glow::after {
    animation: glow 2.8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
</style>
